commit_list.message:
Initial front-end interface hacked together :

 * Ability to add resume URIs;
 * Ability to browse Organizations and Resumes;
 * Fixed bug where invalid URIs would break everything.

Added support for .url, .skills and .skill elements.

* .url links are parsed for the Person's vCard;
* Multiple .skill elements, and .skills elements are parsed and Skill objects created for the relevant Person.
